ContainedObjects.Name: Custom_Tile
ContainedObjects.Description:
Limit 1 Lava per space.

When a Hero enters a Lava Space on a Map Tile, they must immediately roll a D6 (or two D6 and choose if Agility 4 or higher). If the roll is 5+ (the number indicated on the marker), the Hero is safe. If not, the Hero takes D3 Burning Markers.

No test for Heroes starting in a Lava Space.

Enemies do not test for Lava Spaces.

ContainedObjects.Name: Custom_Model_Stack
ContainedObjects.Description:
When a model has one or more Burning Markers on it at the start of its Activation, remove one of those Burning Markers and the model takes 2 Wounds, ignoring Defense.

Only ONE Burning Marker is removed each Activation, so a model may continue to burn for several turns.
